These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: mystery, romance
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | mystery |

 #################################
 
